text: Rivière aux Outardes or Rivière-aux-Outardes (French for "Geese River") may refer to the following rivers and place all in Quebec, Canada: * Rivière aux Outardes (North Shore), river in Côte-Nord region * Rivière aux Outardes (Chateauguay River), a stream in Montérégie ** Rivière aux Outardes Est, a tributary of above * Rivière aux Outardes (Saguenay River), a stream in Saguenay–Lac-Saint-Jean * Rivière-aux-Outardes, Quebec, an unorganized territory in Côte-Nord ==See also== * Outarde (disambiguation)
title: Rivière aux Outardes
